  "texts": [
    "By comparing the F1 score in Table 8, JET-ACOS showed better results on the REST-ACOS, and TAS-BERT-ACOS performed better on the LAPTOP-ACOS.",
    "To adapt TAS-BERT to the ACOSQE extraction task on QUAD-Dataset, Zhang et al. (2021a) changed its tagging schema to predict aspect and opinion terms simultaneously for constructing a unified model to predict the quad, denoted as TASO-TAS with Opinion (Unified).",
    "TASO can be split into two models.",
    "The first model, TASO-BERT-Linear, uses BERT for feature extraction and a linear layer for classification.",
    "The second model, TASO-BERT-CRF, extends the previous model by adding a Conditional Random Field (CRF) layer on top of the TASO-BERT-Linear model."
